data.description: Looking for a short commute to outdoor entertainment near the Riverwalk or room to relax in your oversized backyard with covered patio?  This 3 bed/1 bath home boasts a cozy living room complete with a beautiful fireplace surrounded by built-ins and plenty of room to place your big screen. The carpet in the living room is ALL BRAND NEW!  Don't wait too long as this deal even includes an oversized two car garage just perfect for bringing your vehicles in from the approaching weather.  ALL REASONABLE OFFERS WILL BE CONSIDERED.  Contact SHOWINGTIME at 1-800-746-9464 to schedule your appointment today!   AAAAND GUESS WHAT ELSE!  A MATTERPORT 3-D TOUR!  ENJOY!
